


User
- id
- name
- email
- password
- role (ADMIN | TEACHER | STUDENT)

Student
- class_id


Teacher
(no attributes)


Class
- id
- name


Sprint
- id
- name
- duration
- order (place between another sprints)


Competence
- id
- code (C1, C2, ...)
- label (html/css ..)


Brief
- id
- title
- description
- estimated_duration
- type (INDIVIDUAL | GROUP)
- sprint_id
- class_id
- teacher_id


Submission
- id
- student_id
- brief_id
- content
- submitted_at


Evaluation
- id
- student_id
- brief_id
- competence_id
- teacher_id
- level (ENUM)(IMITER | S_ADAPTER | TRANSPOSER)
- comment
- evaluated_at




---------------------------------
